  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Wilderness Hotel Juutua is offered on a full board basis with breakfast, lunch and dinner included in your stay. </p>
<p>Meals are served in the Aanaar restaurant, which values fine dining and tells the story of the northern wilderness through award-winning cuisine. </p>
<p>The kitchen creates dishes unique to Lapland, so you can expect to try some of the local cuisine during your stay, including fish from Lake Inari. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
